        <h1>Google Ads Management for Small Businesses: What It Costs, What&rsquo;s Included &amp; How to Get Real ROI</h1>
        <div class="post-meta">
          <span>By <strong>Kevin Freeland</strong></span>
          <span>March 13, 2026</span>
          <span>10 min read</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="post-featured-img">
